{
  "stem": "1316.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He made a copy and left a copy in the Jewish Historic Institute in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was lying there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was quoted here and there-- in quotation-- part chapters in the [NON-ENGLISH], in the memorial book.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in 1939, they published it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, one more, let me add, the sister Tama came there to the village, to the auntie.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To the-- to the auntie.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she told her about my mother-- that my mother left her-- a neighbor told my mother left.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was shot there on the spot, together with others.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Tama-- she arranged Tama with another farmer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what he did-- the farmer did-- she sent her to trade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a working labor camp of Czech Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were very well off, with nice clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the farmers traded for food over the-- over the fence for food-- for clothes, for watches, and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She sent Tama to trade it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some guard recognized her, he chased her, and he shot her before the doors.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What he tells there is that after they sent away after the 9th and sent away the 8,000, about 4,000 were collected and gathered from basements, from attics, and so on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were put in the Jewish police station under the outside, in the open.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the people we're singing, and crying, and praying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Twice a week, the gendarmeria came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they dug up mass graves, and they shot them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would--he witnessed all this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the Jewish policemen were busy to cleaning the ghetto, and son.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Poles, right away when the ghetto was out, the Poles robbed-- they attacked the place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took whatever-- they dragged out whatever they could-- clothes and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
